.page-title.default.sizing-banner
  .container
    .page-title--details
      h1.no-padding-bottom
        | Size Guide

.page-content.size-guide-lp
  .container
    .row.head-row
      .col-md-12
        p.head.text-center OUR FIT GUARANTEE
        p.text-center.wrong-size Wrong Size? Exchange for free. It's that simple.
    .row.measurement-row
      .col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12.text-col
        h2.head How to take your measurements
        p We recommend measuring yourself in your underwear, and if possible, the bra you will be wearing with the dress.  It's much more accurate if your measurements are taken by someone else - so get ready to get intimate!
        p
          b Bust
          | : Measure around the fullest part of your bust.
        p
          b Underbust
          | : Measure under your bust, around your rib cage - where your bra band comfortably sits.
        p
          b Waist
          | : Measure around your natural waistline â€“ the smallest part of your waist.
        p
          b Hips
          | : Measure 20cm below your waistline at the fullest part of your hips, with your heels together.
        p
          b Dress length
          | : Stand with your heels together, keeping the tape straight and perpendicular to the floor and measure from your shoulders.
        p
          b Skirt length
          | : Stand with your heels together, keeping the tape straight and perpendicular to the floor. Measure from your natural waistline.
      .col-md-6.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
        /p VIDEO
        = image_tag 'sizing-video.jpg'
    .row
      .col-md-12
        h2 New size guide
        p Some styles follow our brand new size guide, which makes it easier than ever to create a dress with an absolutely flawless fit. Look for a note on each product page to find out if the piece you've been eyeing follows the new or legacy size guide. If you've shopped with us before, your size may have changed.

      .container
        .row.size-guide-row
          .col-md-12
            = render partial: '/products/details/size_chart_table', locals: { data: SizeChart::SIZE_CHART_2016_v2 , size_col_span: 2}

    .row
      .col-md-12
        h2 Legacy size guide
        p Look for a note on each product page to find out if the piece you've been eyeing follows the new or legacy size guide.

      .container
        .row.size-guide-row
          .col-md-12
            = render partial: '/products/details/size_chart_table', locals: { data: SizeChart::SIZE_CHART_2016 , size_col_span: 2}

    .row.advice-fit
      .col-md-12
        h2.h3.text-center Want advice on fit and style ?
        .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.text-center
          p Let Fame style you--for free. Our wardrobe stylist Amber Bond is available to advise on fit, customization, and styling options via chat, phone, or video call. It's that easy.

        .col-md-12.text-center
          = link_to styling_session_path
            span.btn-xs.btn-featured
              | Book Your Session
